<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha384-k6RqeWeci5ZR/Lv4MR0sA0FfDOMht/RPxOHjFnlHhLvByDU0s9dH9/fS8KXr25uH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.7.1/dist/leaflet.css" />
    <style>
        .rounded-circle {
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        #map {
            height: 300px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="text-center my-5">
        <div class="display-6 border-bottom pb-3">Contact Us</div>
        <div class="lead mt-5">
            <div class="my-4">
                <i class="fa fa-phone bg-secondary text-white p-3 rounded-circle"></i>
                <p class="mt-3">
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="my-4">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-address-book bg-secondary text-white p-3 rounded-circle"></i>
                <p class="mt-3">
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Aut, blanditiis dolorem, eveniet itaque odio laborum doloremque reiciendis laboriosam dolorum tempore optio qui maiores voluptates sapiente dolor labore assumenda. Culpa, commodi.
                    Officia vel deserunt velit mollitia neque aut possimus perferendis. Eos nihil est aperiam labore similique at deleniti harum repellat eaque, reiciendis doloremque quos voluptatum earum consectetur amet nemo illum optio?
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="my-4">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope bg-secondary text-white p-3 rounded-circle"></i>
                <p class="mt-3">
                    Lorem ipsum dolor
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="my-4">
                <div class="border p-3 rounded">
                    <div id="map"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.7.1/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            var map = L.map('map').setView([51.505, -0.09], 13); // Default view set to London

            L.tileLayer('https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png', {
                attribution: 'Â© OpenStreetMap contributors'
            }).addTo(map);

            var lat = (Math.random() * 180) - 90;  // Random latitude between -90 and 90
            var lng = (Math.random() * 360) - 180; // Random longitude between -180 and 180
            var randomLocation = [lat, lng];

            map.setView(randomLocation, 3);

            L.marker(randomLocation).addTo(map)
                .bindPopup('Random Location')
                .openPopup();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
